fresh, healthy produce for our Cathedral Kitchen meal program, is back for a 
second year. Our first task is to prepare the soil for planting. We will have 
our first work party of the year on Saturday, March 14, from 9:00 to noon, to 
spread compost and to do other soil preparation work. We need about 20 people to 
get the job done, so please join us and bring your friends. For information, or 
to volunteer for this work party or throughout the year, contact
<a href="mailto:alpinist@comcast.net?subject=Cathedral Kitchen Garden Work Party">
Gary</a>.</p>
