<p><strong>THE CATHEDRAL ESPRESSO CART</strong> is up and running!
Your friendly Cathedral baristas will be serving
espresso drinks after the 10:00 Mass. During the month
of March, all proceeds benefit the Cathedral Kitchen
Garden.</p>
