Pro Musica presents a tribute to great female
composers throughout the centuries. <em>Information</em>, 206-781-2766 or 
<a href="http://www.seattlepromusica.org" target="_bulletin">www.seattlepromusica.org</a>.</p>
<p><strong>PARISH REMEMBRANCE</strong>: <em>Throughout the year, because we
